chamado Seth.

569
00:37:28,079 --> 00:37:30,081
-Acha que ela gostou dela?
-Sua mãe?

570
00:37:30,165 --> 00:37:31,875
-Sim.
-Claro.

571
00:37:34,961 --> 00:37:36,921
