673
00:44:18,573 --> 00:44:19,574
Sim.

674
00:44:23,494 --> 00:44:24,495
Ty?

675
00:44:26,622 --> 00:44:27,748
Querido?

676
00:44:30,543 --> 00:44:31,544
Ty.

677
00:44:33,129 --> 00:44:33,963
Ty.

